RELATED() ‚Üí Use when enriching the Sales fact table with lookup attributes (e.g., Product Category, Customer Region).

RELATEDTABLE() ‚Üí Use when calculating from the lookup/dimension table by pulling 
related fact rows (e.g., count sales per product, total revenue per customer).

